  "title": "Tapping for debt obsession",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute script for the loop of replaying balances and feeling defined by what you owe.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 6 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program. The script targets the debt-obsession loop: checking the balance, replaying the interest numbers, feeling like the debt is a permanent verdict on who you are. Use when the debt thinking has taken over the day, not when planning a repayment.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 6 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"Stop obsessing over debt.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
