        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 6 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program. The script targets the debt-obsession loop: the constant replaying of balances and interest, the feeling that the debt defines you, the weight of owing. Use it when the thinking has taken over, not when reviewing the numbers to plan a repayment.",
            "type": "text"
          }
